<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>影梦 Silhouette Dream - 游戏百科</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=Silkscreen:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* 像素风格色彩 - 复古游戏机调色板 */
            --pixel-blue: #5D6BA3;
            --pixel-teal: #4A7B5D;
            --pixel-cream: #B8A86C;
            --pixel-white: #E0D8B0;
            --pixel-gray: #8A8580;
            --pixel-green: #3A7545;
            --pixel-red: #A34A4A;
            --pixel-gold: #B8A86C;
            --pixel-purple: #7A6B7C;
            
            --bg-primary: #0A0A14;
            --bg-secondary: #1A1A24;
            --bg-tertiary: #2A2A34;
            --text-primary: #E0E0FF;
            --text-secondary: #A0A0C0;
            --accent: #5D6BA3;
            --accent-glow: rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.4);
            
            /* 像素网格 */
            --pixel-size: 4px;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Silkscreen', 'Press Start 2P', 'Noto Sans SC', monospace;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.5;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            image-rendering: pixelated;
            image-rendering: crisp-edges;
        }

        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--pixel-blue);
            border-radius: 0;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--pixel-teal);
        }

        /* Blur Effect - 仅对标题使用 */
        .blur-dream {
            filter: blur(0.3px);
        }

        /* Pixel Glass - 像素风格玻璃效果 */
        .glass {
            background: rgba(42, 42, 52, 0.95);
            border: 2px solid var(--pixel-blue);
            border-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pixel-blue), var(--pixel-teal) 4px) 2;
        }

        .glass-strong {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 36, 0.98);
            border: 2px solid var(--pixel-teal);
            border-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pixel-teal), var(--pixel-blue) 4px) 2;
        }

        /* Pixel Gradient Text - 像素风格渐变文字 */
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pixel-blue) 0%, var(--pixel-teal) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            image-rendering: pixelated;
        }

        .gradient-text-purple {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pixel-purple) 0%, var(--pixel-blue) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            image-rendering: pixelated;
        }

        /* Pixel Glow Effects - 像素风格发光效果 */
        .glow {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--pixel-blue), 0 0 0 4px var(--pixel-teal);
        }

        .glow-text {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--pixel-blue), 4px 4px 0 var(--pixel-teal);
        }

        /* Pixel Card Hover Effects */
        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--pixel-blue), 8px 8px 0 var(--pixel-teal);
            border-color: var(--pixel-blue);
        }

        /* Pixel Navigation */
        .nav-link {
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 var(--pixel-blue);
        }
        .nav-link::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--pixel-blue);
            transition: width 0.2s ease;
        }
        .nav-link:hover::after,
        .nav-link.active::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Pixel Section Divider */
        .section-divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pixel-blue), var(--pixel-teal) 4px);
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        /* Pixel Tag Styles */
        .tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 0;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border: 2px solid var(--pixel-blue);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: rgba(42, 42, 52, 0.9);
        }
        .tag:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--pixel-teal), 4px 4px 0 var(--pixel-blue);
            border-color: var(--pixel-teal);
        }

        /* Mermaid Diagrams */
        .mermaid {
            background: transparent !important;
        }

        /* Pixel Grid Pattern Background */
        .grid-pattern {
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 32px 32px;
            image-rendering: pixelated;
        }

        /* Enhanced Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 0px, rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 32px, transparent 32px, transparent 64px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 0px, rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.1) 32px, transparent 32px, transparent 64px);
            image-rendering: pixelated;
        }

        /* Pixel Floating Elements */
        .float-element {
            animation: pixelFloat 10s steps(10) infinite;
            opacity: 0.3;
            will-change: transform;
            image-rendering: pixelated;
        }
        .float-element:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: -3s; }
        .float-element:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: -6s; }

        @keyframes pixelFloat {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-16px); }
        }

        /* Timeline - 怀旧时间线 */
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            border-left: 1px solid rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.3);
        }
        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -4px;
            top: 0.5rem;
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #6B7B8C;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.4);
        }

        /* Character Card */
        .character-card {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .character-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.9) 100%);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .character-card-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Enhanced Tab System */
        .tab-btn {
            position: relative;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            opacity: 0.6;
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .tab-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.1), transparent);
            transition: left 0.6s ease;
        }
        .tab-btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .tab-btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }
        .tab-btn.active {
            color: #9A9085;
            border-bottom-color: #9A9085;
            opacity: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.2);
        }
        .tab-content {
            display: none;
        }
        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% { opacity: 0; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Enhanced Progress Bar */
        .progress-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.2);
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        .progress-bar::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3), transparent);
            animation: progressShine 2s infinite;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6B7B8C, #5A6B5C);
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: width 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        @keyframes progressShine {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateX(100%);
            }
        }

        /* Stat Card - 朦胧卡片 */
        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(26, 26, 37, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid rgba(184, 176, 168, 0.05);
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7B8C, #5A6B5C);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            filter: saturate(0.8);
        }

        /* Mobile Menu */
        .mobile-menu {
            transform: translateX(-100%);
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }
        .mobile-menu.open {
            transform: translateX(0);
        }

        /* Pixel Color Classes */
        .text-pixel-blue { color: #5D6BA3; }
        .text-pixel-teal { color: #4A7B5D; }
        .text-pixel-cream { color: #B8A86C; }
        .text-pixel-white { color: #E0D8B0; }
        .text-pixel-gray { color: #8A8580; }
        .text-pixel-green { color: #3A7545; }
        .text-pixel-red { color: #A34A4A; }
        .text-pixel-gold { color: #B8A86C; }
        .text-pixel-purple { color: #7A6B7C; }

        .bg-pixel-blue { background-color: rgba(93, 107, 163, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-teal { background-color: rgba(74, 123, 93, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-cream { background-color: rgba(184, 168, 108, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-white { background-color: rgba(224, 216, 176, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-gray { background-color: rgba(138, 133, 128, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-green { background-color: rgba(58, 117, 69, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-red { background-color: rgba(163, 74, 74, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-gold { background-color: rgba(184, 168, 108, 0.3); }
        .bg-pixel-purple { background-color: rgba(122, 107, 124, 0.3); }

        .border-pixel-blue { border-color: #5D6BA3; }
        .border-pixel-teal { border-color: #4A7B5D; }
        .border-pixel-cream { border-color: #B8A86C; }
        .border-pixel-white { border-color: #E0D8B0; }
        .border-pixel-gray { border-color: #8A8580; }
        .border-pixel-green { border-color: #3A7545; }
        .border-pixel-red { border-color: #A34A4A; }
        .border-pixel-gold { border-color: #B8A86C; }
        .border-pixel-purple { border-color: #7A6B7C; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="grid-pattern">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 glass-strong">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <a href="#hero" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7B8C, #5A6B5C);">
                        <i class="fas fa-moon text-white text-lg" style="opacity: 0.8;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-serif text-xl font-bold gradient-text">影梦</span>
                </a>
                
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
                    <a href="#world" class="nav-link text-sm" style="color: #B8B0A8;">世界观</a>
                    <a href="#characters" class="nav-link text-sm" style="color: #B8B0A8;">角色</a>
                    <a href="#gameplay" class="nav-link text-sm" style="color: #B8B0A8;">玩法</a>
                    <a href="#art" class="nav-link text-sm" style="color: #B8B0A8;">美术</a>
                    <a href="#concept" class="nav-link text-sm" style="color: #B8B0A8;">概念</a>
                </div>

                <button id="mobileMenuBtn" class="md:hidden" style="color: #B8B0A8;">
                    <i class="fas fa-bars text-xl"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Mobile Menu -->
    <div id="mobileMenu" class="mobile-menu fixed inset-0 z-40 glass-strong pt-20 px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
            <a href="#world" class="text-lg py-2 border-b border-white/10" style="color: #B8B0A8;">世界观</a>
            <a href="#characters" class="text-lg py-2 border-b border-white/10" style="color: #B8B0A8;">角色</a>
            <a href="#gameplay" class="text-lg py-2 border-b border-white/10" style="color: #B8B0A8;">玩法</a>
            <a href="#art" class="text-lg py-2 border-b border-white/10" style="color: #B8B0A8;">美术</a>
            <a href="#concept" class="text-lg py-2 border-b border-white/10" style="color: #B8B0A8;">概念</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="hero" class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
            <div class="float-element absolute top-20 left-10 w-32 h-32 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.15);"></div>
            <div class="float-element absolute top-40 right-20 w-48 h-48 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: rgba(90, 107, 92, 0.1);"></div>
            <div class="float-element absolute bottom-32 left-1/4 w-40 h-40 rounded-full blur-3xl" style="background: rgba(138, 133, 128, 0.08);"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full animate-pulse" style="background: #5A6B5C;"></span>
                <span class="text-xs tracking-wider" style="color: #9A9085;">开发中</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="hero-title font-serif text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight blur-dream">
                <span class="gradient-text glow-text">影梦</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4 font-light tracking-wide" style="color: #9A9085;">
                Silhouette Dream
            </p>
            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-lg" style="color: #8A8580;">
                当黑夜降临，影子开始它的旅程
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#world" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-white font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-lg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7B8C, #5A6B5C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.3);">
                    探索世界
                </a>
                <a href="#concept" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg glass font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-all" style="color: #B8B0A8;">
                    核心概念
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Stats -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">4</div>
                    <div class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: #8A8580;">梦境层级</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">12</div>
                    <div class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: #8A8580;">特色区域</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">3</div>
                    <div class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: #8A8580;">主要角色</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number">∞</div>
                    <div class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: #8A8580;">可能性</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce" style="color: #7A7570;">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- World View Section -->
    <section id="world" class="py-24 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="tag glass text-millennium-blue mb-4">WORLD VIEW</span>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #B8B0A8;">世界观</h2>
                <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #8A8580;">
                    在永恒太阳衰败之后，影子一族必须在黑夜中寻找生存之道
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Origin Story -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold gradient-text">世界起源</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4" style="color: #9A9085;">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">远古时代</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm">永恒太阳持续照耀，影子一族建立繁荣文明</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">太阳衰败</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm">黑夜诞生，影子面临消逝危机</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">现代时空</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm">影子与人类形成共生关系，通过梦境连接</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover">
                    <div class="mermaid">
graph TB
    A[永恒太阳时代] --> B[太阳衰败]
    B --> C[影子危机]
    C --> D[依附人类]
    D --> E[梦境连接]
    E --> F[共生时代]
    
    style A fill:#6B7B8C,stroke:#6B7B8C,color:#fff
    style F fill:#5A6B5C,stroke:#5A6B5C,color:#fff
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dream World Layers -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center" style="color: #B8B0A8;">梦境层级</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-millennium-blue">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-millennium-blue">
                            <i class="fas fa-sun text-millennium-blue text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">清醒期</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">Hypnagogic State</p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-3" style="color: #9A9085;">准备阶段，路线选择与情报收集</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-millennium-teal">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-millennium-teal">
                            <i class="fas fa-eye text-millennium-teal text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">快速眼动期</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">REM Phase</p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-3" style="color: #9A9085;">核心战斗与探索，情绪怪物活跃</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-millennium-gold">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-millennium-gold">
                            <i class="fas fa-water text-millennium-gold text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">浅睡期</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">Light Sleep</p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-3" style="color: #9A9085;">过渡区域，解谜与收集</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border-t-4 border-millennium-rust">
