                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-millennium-teal">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain text-millennium-teal text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">情绪投射</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">现实情绪具象化为梦境实体，影响怪物生成</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 bg-millennium-gold">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt text-millennium-gold text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">光能系统</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">影子依靠光而存在，黑暗中逐渐失去自我</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.3);">
                        <i class="fas fa-puzzle-piece text-xl" style="color: #9A8A9A;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">解谜机制</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">利用光线、影子和环境互动解决谜题</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.2);">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-peace text-millennium-blue text-xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">无战斗设计</h4>
