                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">教室</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(160, 144, 112, 0.2); color: #9A8A6A;">涂鸦</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-cream">宣传栏</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.2), rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.2));">
                        <i class="fas fa-dungeon text-6xl" style="color: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.4);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">废弃游乐场</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            褪色的旋转木马，生锈的滑梯，停止的音乐，杂草丛生的秋千
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.2); color: #9A8A9A;">旋转木马</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-moss">杂草</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">生锈</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.3), rgba(90, 107, 92, 0.1));">
                        <i class="fas fa-hospital text-6xl" style="color: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.5);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">废弃小诊所</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            褪色的白色瓷砖，生锈的医疗器械，墙上的药品广告已经模糊不清
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-white">白色瓷砖</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">医疗器械</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-blue">药品广告</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.3), rgba(107, 74, 60, 0.2));">
                        <i class="fas fa-theater-masks text-6xl" style="color: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.5);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">废弃图书馆/大剧院</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            落满灰尘的书架，破损的舞台幕布，褪色的红色座椅，寂静的阅读区
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">书架</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-gold">舞台</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-cream">座椅</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a20, #0a0a0f);">
                        <i class="fas fa-home text-6xl" style="color: rgba(90, 90, 95, 0.4);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">小男孩的家</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            破旧但温馨，墙上贴着画作，桌上摆放着简单晚餐，床头放着旧泰迪熊
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(139, 119, 89, 0.2); color: #8B7759;">泰迪熊</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-gold">画作</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(184, 176, 168, 0.1); color: #9A9A9A;">温馨</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.15), rgba(90, 107, 92, 0.1));">
                        <i class="fas fa-clinic-medical text-6xl" style="color: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.5);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">废弃小诊所</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            医生的据点，褪色的蓝白招牌，生锈的铁门，里面却整洁有序。药柜上的玻璃瓶反射着微弱的光。
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-blue">医生据点</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(184, 176, 168, 0.2); color: #B8B0A8;">药柜</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">铁门</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 107, 92, 0.2), rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.15));">
                        <i class="fas fa-book text-6xl" style="color: rgba(90, 107, 92, 0.5);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">破旧图书馆</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            外墙爬满爬山虎，内部却意外完好。发黄但不破烂的旧书，亮着的电灯，仿佛有人一直在维护。休息据点，可回复体力、平静内心。
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-teal">休息据点</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(154, 144, 133, 0.2); color: #9A9085;">旧书</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-moss">爬山虎</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(160, 144, 112, 0.2); color: #A09070;">旧而不破</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden card-hover">
                    <div class="h-48 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 74, 60, 0.15), rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.2));">
                        <i class="fas fa-tree text-6xl" style="color: rgba(107, 74, 60, 0.4);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2" style="color: #B8B0A8;">小区公园</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #7A7570;">
                            大象滑梯，紫藤花长廊，常见健身器材。对内向社恐的小男孩来说，这里不是美好回忆的地方，而是遭受排挤与嘲笑的场所。
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(107, 74, 60, 0.2); color: #8B6A5C;">负面回忆</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-moss">紫藤花</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs" style="background: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.2); color: #9A8A9A;">大象滑梯</span>
                            <span class="tag text-xs text-millennium-rust">孤独</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Visual Keywords -->
            <div class="mt-12 glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #B8B0A8;">视觉关键词</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">褪色的蓝/绿玻璃</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">白色瓷砖贴片</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">灰色马赛克水磨石</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">几何形外立面</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">旋转楼梯</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">人去楼空</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">破旧不堪</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">玻璃碎片</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">厚厚灰尘</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">童年物品</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">发白的家具</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">褪色装饰</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">未完成日常</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">朦胧失真</span>
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass" style="color: #9A9085;">怀旧恍惚</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider max-w-4xl mx-auto"></div>

    <!-- Concept Section -->
    <section id="concept" class="py-24 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="tag glass mb-4" style="color: #9A8A9A;">CONCEPT</span>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #B8B0A8;">核心概念</h2>
                <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #8A8580;">
                    游戏设计的理论基础，支撑故事叙述和系统实现
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Core Concepts -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 card-hover text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(40, 40, 50, 0.8);">
                        <i class="fas fa-ghost text-3xl" style="color: #6a6a75;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #B8B0A8;">影子与光</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">影子的存在依赖光，在黑暗中逐渐失去自我。光不仅是视觉元素，更是生命、记忆和身份的象征。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 card-hover text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(107, 123, 140, 0.2);">
                        <i class="fas fa-moon text-3xl text-millennium-blue"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #B8B0A8;">梦境与现实</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">梦境是现实的投射，也是逃避现实的庇护所。两个世界相互影响，形成独特的叙事结构。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 card-hover text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.2);">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart-broken text-3xl" style="color: #9A8A9A;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #B8B0A8;">孤独与连接</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">孤独是普遍的情感，连接是治愈孤独的良药。游戏通过角色关系探索这一永恒主题。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Design Pillars -->
            <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #B8B0A8;">设计支柱</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-millennium-blue">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">1</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">情感共鸣</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">通过真实的情感体验与玩家建立深层连接，而非单纯的游戏机制</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-millennium-teal">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">2</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">氛围沉浸</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">千禧年梦核美学，朦胧失真的视觉风格，唤起怀旧与孤独感</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-millennium-gold">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">3</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">叙事驱动</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">故事是核心，玩法服务于叙事，每个机制都有叙事意义</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(107, 74, 60, 0.3);">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">4</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">象征隐喻</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">游戏元素承载深层含义，影子、光、梦境都是象征载体</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(90, 80, 95, 0.3);">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">5</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">成长蜕变</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">角色在游戏过程中经历内心成长，玩家见证并参与这一过程</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(154, 144, 133, 0.3);">
                                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">6</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #B8B0A8;">诗意留白</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #9A9085;">不过度解释，给玩家想象空间，让情感在留白中发酵</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t" style="border-color: rgba(184, 176, 168, 0.1);">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B7B8C, #5A6B5C);">
                        <i class="fas fa-moon text-white text-lg" style="opacity: 0.8;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-serif text-xl font-bold gradient-text">影梦</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm" style="color: #7A7570;">
                    Silhouette Dream Wiki v3.0 | 千禧年梦核风格
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg glass flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors" style="color: #9A9085;">
                        <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg glass flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors" style="color: #9A9085;">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Initialize Mermaid
        mermaid.initialize({
            startOnLoad: true,
            theme: 'dark',
            themeVariables: {
                primaryColor: '#6B7B8C',
                primaryTextColor: '#fff',
                primaryBorderColor: '#6B7B8C',
                lineColor: '#7A7570',
                secondaryColor: '#5A6B5C',
                tertiaryColor: '#1a1a25'
            }
        });

        // Tab System
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const tabId = btn.dataset.tab;
                
                // Remove active class from all tabs and content
                document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
                
                // Add active class to clicked tab and corresponding content
                btn.classList.add('active');
                document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');
            });
        });

        // Mobile Menu
        const mobileMenuBtn = document.getElementById('mobileMenuBtn');
        const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
        
        mobileMenuBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            mobileMenu.classList.toggle('open');
        });

        // Close mobile menu when clicking a link
        mobileMenu.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(link => {
            link.addEventListener('click', () => {
                mobileMenu.classList.remove('open');
            });
        });

        // Smooth scroll for navigation links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
                if (target) {
                    target.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth',
                        block: 'start'
                    });
                }
            });
        });

        // Active navigation link on scroll - 使用 IntersectionObserver 替代 scroll 监听
        const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');
        const sectionObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    const id = entry.target.getAttribute('id');
                    navLinks.forEach(link => {
                        link.classList.remove('active');
                        if (link.getAttribute('href') === '#' + id) {
                            link.classList.add('active');
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
        }, { threshold: 0.3 });

        document.querySelectorAll('section[id]').forEach(section => {
            sectionObserver.observe(section);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>